data.description: Adorable Craftsman/Bungalow style home in the heart of downtown Springfield! Directly across from the Innovation Academy a STEAM Magnet school and walking distance to Garner Street Park! This house has all the charm of a historic home with tons of modern upgrades. Featuring a large foyer with the original Antique sliding door, 2 fireplaces, 3 large bedrooms and 2 full newly remodeled baths. Host family and holidays meals in your Victorian style dining room with fireplace. This house has a charming eat-in country kitchen with tons of counter space and newer stainless steel appliance,  also recently remodeled. HVAC less than 1yr old, ROOF is under 5 yrs. Enjoy your Southern Front Porch or your freshly painted screened in back porch! Need a work space or extra storage? This home has a detached 1 car garage plus workshop/storage room! Plus a fenced yard for your pets or kids! Plenty of space in the driveway for family and friends!
